OL,3,C'Hero' bus driver says he wants
OL,4,Capology after he was sacked after
OL,5,Ccatching thief
OL,7,FA bus driver who was sacked after he
OL,8,Fchased down a thief to return a
OL,9,Fpassenger's stolen necklace said he
OL,10,Fwould "be very happy" if Metroline
OL,11,Fapologised ` but does not want to
OL,12,Freturn to his job.
OL,14,FMore than 100,000 people have signed a
OL,15,Fpetition to support Mark Hehir, 62,
OL,16,Fwho was sacked after he chased a thief
OL,17,Fwho stole a passenger's necklace
OL,18,Fbefore knocking them out in self-
OL,19,Fdefence when they returned.
