OL,5,Ccatching thief
OL,7,FMr Hehir, who worked in north-west
OL,8,FLondon but is originally from
OL,9,FLimerick, Ireland, said the support
OL,10,Ffrom the public has been "incredible"
OL,11,Fsince an employment tribunal upheld
OL,12,FMetrolink's decision, a ruling first
OL,13,Freported by the Press Association.
OL,15,F"I'd be very happy if Metroline made
OL,16,Fan apology and just admitted that they
OL,17,Fmight have got it wrong.
