OL,3,C'Hero' bus driver says he wants
OL,4,Capology after he was sacked after
OL,5,Ccatching thief
OL,7,F"I'd like them to compensate me for
OL,8,Flost earnings, that's important, that
OL,9,Fthey understand they got it wrong,
OL,10,Fthat's important for me," he told the
OL,11,FPress Association.
OL,13,FAsked if he would accept his job back,
OL,14,FMr Hehir said: "Absolutely not, you
OL,15,Fcannot work for a company that treats
OL,16,Fits staff like that.
OL,18,F"I'm not saying they treat the drivers
OL,19,Fbad, I'm just saying if anything does
OL,20,Fhappen, it's always the driver's
OL,21,Ffault, they'll come down on you heavy.
