OL,7,F"You're on your own, you've created a
OL,8,Fsituation, now you get out of it,
OL,9,Fthere's no help."
OL,11,FMr Hehir, who described driving a bus
OL,12,Fas "an underpaid tough job", said the
OL,13,Fsupport he has received online has
OL,14,Fbeen "incredible" but he does not
OL,15,Fthink of himself as a "hero".
OL,17,F"I've always felt I was justified in
OL,18,Fmy actions, and it just seems that
OL,19,F99.5% of people agree with me," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
