OL,7,F"I'm actually looking for negative
OL,8,Fresponses, and I just can't find any,
OL,9,FI mean, everywhere there's thousands
OL,10,Fof messages."
OL,12,FAn online petition calling for Mr
OL,13,FHehir to be reinstated or compensated,
OL,14,Flaunched by shadow justice minister Dr
OL,15,FKieran Mullan, has gained more than
OL,16,F100,000 signatures.
OL,18,FA GoFundMe page for Mr Hehir has
OL,19,Fraised more than #20,000.
