OL,7,FHe said that after the 2024 incident
OL,8,F"I spent six days in hospital, because
OL,9,FI got an infection from the guy's
OL,10,Ftooth."
OL,12,F"I ended up in ICU, I had two
OL,13,Foperations on my hand because of the
OL,14,Finfection, I was very, very close to
OL,15,Flosing my hand, I quote the surgeon,
OL,16,Fprobably in the next three days if I
OL,17,Fdidn't get it seen to at the time."
