OL,7,FMr Hehir added: "Even in that time I
OL,8,Fwas still employed by the company, not
OL,9,Fone person from the company, HR or
OL,10,Fanyone else, rang me to ask how I was,
OL,11,Fand I thought that was a disgrace."
OL,13,FHe added: "Now I did get some help
OL,14,Ffrom the union, but that can only go
OL,15,Fso far."
OL,17,FMr Hehir, who currently works in a
OL,18,Fbar, said he was in bed when his story
OL,19,Fwent online: "I didn't know what was
OL,20,Fgoing on, but then my phone just
OL,21,Fstarted popping, going crazy."
