OL,10,Fthief says it all about the wet, woke,
OL,11,Flegalistic pettifoggers who run
OL,12,FStarmer's Britain."
OL,14,FReform UK MP Robert Jenrick posted on
OL,15,FX: "Metroline should reinstate Mark
OL,16,Fand apologise for their disgraceful
OL,17,Fconduct."
OL,19,FA Metroline spokesperson said: "The
OL,20,Ftribunal has upheld the dismissal as
OL,21,Ffair."
